    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_4_841-976",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "841-976",
      "markText": "自伯特(Burt，1984)在美国综合社会调查项目(General Social Survey Project)中首次运用“重要问题的讨论网”的提名技术(name generator)研究人们的社会网络特征以来，“重要问题的讨论网”成为网络分析者经常涉猎的重要领域之一。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=841&rangeEnd=976",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=841&rangeEnd=976"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_5_2160-2227",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2160-2227",
      "markText": "与传统社会学分析的逻辑相异，不是从可观察世界的先验分类进入一组具体的范畴，而是从一组关系出发，从这些关系中推演出社会结构的形态和类型。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2160&rangeEnd=2227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2160&rangeEnd=2227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_5_5038-5110",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5038-5110",
      "markText": "他们否认分析可以在彼此分离的独立范畴内（例如，无产阶级和资产阶级、核心和边缘国家等范畴）进行，拒绝把有严格边界的群体视作宏观社会系统的基本构件。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5038&rangeEnd=5110",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5038&rangeEnd=5110"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_5_7569-7603",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7569-7603",
      "markText": "群体密度、群体界限的严密性和群体内外联系的模式规定了资源流动的方式。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7569&rangeEnd=7603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7569&rangeEnd=7603"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_1558-1624",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1558-1624",
      "markText": "他希望对社会结构进行重新界定，不同社会地位和群体人口分布之外的心理需求、文化价值、规范、技术力量等因素不应该包括在社会结构的范畴内。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1558&rangeEnd=1624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1558&rangeEnd=1624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_2520-2602",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2520-2602",
      "markText": "他和同事通过分析扬基城家庭小集团的详细资料，发现多数小集团将相同或邻近阶级的人联系起来(Warner and Lunt，1941：110-111、350-355)。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2520&rangeEnd=2602",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2520&rangeEnd=2602"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_3184-3264",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3184-3264",
      "markText": "这个一般假定后来被概括为同质性或类似性原理(Principle of Homogeneity or Similarities)(Laumann，1973：5)。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3184&rangeEnd=3264",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3184&rangeEnd=3264"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_6828-6871",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6828-6871",
      "markText": "另外，具有异质性网络的人不太可能获得一致的初级社会支持和证实这些“特征性”的行为方式。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6828&rangeEnd=6871",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6828&rangeEnd=6871"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_8064-8130",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "8064-8130",
      "markText": "然而，朋友网络的规模，无论是联合的（与妻子一同参与互动）还是性别隔离的，四种同质性网络类型中的平均互动频率并没有呈现任何显著的模式。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8064&rangeEnd=8130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8064&rangeEnd=8130"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_8442-8542",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "8442-8542",
      "markText": "在一般意义上，一个连锁型网络将会由一些在重要社会特征方面类似的人组成，其基础是社会特征的类似势必内含着社会态度和人格特征的类似，因此人们相互吸引(Laumann，1966，1973：113-114)。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8442&rangeEnd=8542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8442&rangeEnd=8542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_8590-8678",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "8590-8678",
      "markText": "一种亲密的面对面关系的显著特征，特别是在没有制度性限制而志愿形成和解体的情况下（在某种意义上，朋友是连续彼此选择的过程），是参与者激烈冲突的最小化或至少是严格地限制激烈的冲突。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8590&rangeEnd=8678",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8590&rangeEnd=8678"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_8692-8729",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "8692-8729",
      "markText": "人们享有相对类似的社会位置，也更可能在工作和私人生活中享有共同的地理空间。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8692&rangeEnd=8729",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8692&rangeEnd=8729"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_9408-9459",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "9408-9459",
      "markText": "许多个人更可能在地理空间和社会位置上流动，以功能上更特殊的标准建立友谊关系会促进个人适应新的社会环境。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9408&rangeEnd=9459",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9408&rangeEnd=9459"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_10088-10165",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10088-10165",
      "markText": "因为从父到子的职业地位变动内含着个人社会交往本质的重大变化，有可能导向更具社会异质性的友谊网络，某些网络在其初始地位时形成，另一些则在他的目标地位时形成。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10088&rangeEnd=10165",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10088&rangeEnd=10165"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_9_11001-11060",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "11001-11060",
      "markText": "内部成员之间“强制推行的信任”，对于金融领域上层精英友谊关系的建立和维持发挥了重要作用(Kadushin，1995)。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11001&rangeEnd=11060",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32650813aba36ag015476?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11001&rangeEnd=11060"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300155945_10_2622-2660",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2622-2660",
      "markText": "因此，他们会考虑（可能并非有意识地）其目前的朋友将对潜在的朋友做出何种反应。",
      "totalCount": 5,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300155945&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2622&rangeEnd=2660",
